text:
Pink... light blue... pale green...
Spring-colored cookies...

These cute sweets...
It feels like a waste to eat them!

Yes! Once you eat them,
you won't be able to see them anymore...!

I was thinking of saving them for today...
Producer said we could all eat them together though...

Though I thought that...
They look so delicious, I think I'll have just a bit!

I want to eat them!
Actually, I'm a little hungry too...

Yes... Just a bit...
of spring colors...
